://www.nme.com/artists/liam-payne">利亚姆·佩恩</a>的死因已通过尸检揭晓，结果显示他死于坠落受伤。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/liam-payne-one-direction-obituary-3803755">Liam Payne 1993-2004：One Direction 明星帮助引发了流行现象</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/one-direction">One Direction</a>歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-directions-liam-payne-had-died-aged-31-3803523">昨天（10 月 16 日）在阿根廷布宜诺斯艾利斯卡萨苏尔巴勒莫酒店从三楼阳台坠落身亡</a>，据<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/music/2024/oct/17/liam-payne-died-of-multiple-traumas-and-internal-and-external-bleeding" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《卫报》</em></a>报道，阿根廷检察官办公室称，他死于多处外伤和内伤。外出血——他的头部受伤严重到足以导致死亡。</p><p>佩恩坠落时被认为是独自一人，他于当地时间下午 5 点左右坠落，酒店的客人告诉<em>《卫报》</em> ，在他坠落前的几个小时里，他们听到了敲击声和喊叫声。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-paynes-911-call-made-by-hotel-employee-revealed-3803631" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>路透社报道</em></a>，该酒店的一名接待员<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-paynes-911-call-made-by-hotel-employee-revealed-3803631">致电当地紧急服务部门，称一名“具有攻击性的男子可能受到毒品和酒精的影响”</a> ，而酒店经理则表示，他听到酒店后面有很大的噪音，警方发现他们抵达时，一名男子从阳台掉入酒店内部庭院。</p><p>在他的房间里查获了表明饮酒和吸毒的物品，警方表示，他们发现房间“完全混乱”，里面有氯硝西泮（一种中枢神经系统抑制剂）、能量补充剂和其他非处方药。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/news/liam-payne-dead-hotel-room-latest-one-direction-b2631055.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《独立报》</em></a>报道，从发现佩恩尸体的庭院中起获了一个威士忌酒瓶、打火机和手机。 </p><figure id="attachment_3803867" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3803867" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3803867" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne-Tributes.jpg" alt="利亚姆·佩恩去世后，粉丝们悼念他" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne-Tributes.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne-Tributes-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne-Tributes-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne-Tributes-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne-Tributes-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Liam-Payne-Tributes-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3803867" class="wp-caption-text">球迷们在阿根廷布宜诺斯艾利斯的卡萨苏尔巴勒莫酒店外向佩恩致敬。图片来源：LUIS ROBAYO/法新社，盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>据<a href="https://www.reuters.com/world/one-direction-singer-liam-payne-found-dead-buenos-aires-local-media-reports-2024-10-16/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>路透社</em></a>和<a href="https://www.gmanetwork.com/news/showbiz/showbizabroad/923975/one-direction-singer-liam-payne-found-dead-in-buenos-aires-local-media-reports/story/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>GMA News</em></a>报道，布宜诺斯艾利斯报纸<em>La Nacion</em>最先报道了佩恩去世的消息，随后<em>美国有线电视新闻网 (CNN)</em>通过地方当局的声明证实了这一消息。</p><p>来自音乐界和娱乐界的人物纷纷向这位歌手致敬，他于 2010 年与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/harry-styles">Harry Styles</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zayn-malik">Zayn Malik</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/niall-horan">Niall Horan</a>一起成为有史以来最畅销的男孩乐队 One Direction 的五分之一。和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/louis-tomlinson">路易斯·汤姆林森</a>。</p><p>斯泰尔斯的母亲在 Instagram 上写道，佩恩“只是一个男孩”，而马利克的妹妹则说：“我简直不敢相信，老实说，我对这个悲伤的时刻无话可说……我真的不敢相信。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DBNIp_1ITDv/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-righ